----------------------------
FeTA 2.0 - Release 03.05.2021
Release of the dataset for the FeTA Challenge, MICCAI 2021
----------------------------
FeTA 2.1 - release 27.05.2021
Subjects 001-040: .json files updated to contain more accurate resolution information
Subjects 041-080: Images (*T2w.nii.gz) and Label annotations (*dseg.nii.gz) updated: 
			-The resolution of all files is now 0.5x0.5x0.5mm^3
			-Erroneous label numbers (ex Label 13) removed
			-Label annotations were corrected
----------------------------
FeTA 2.2 - release 01.06.2021
Subjects 047, 065: Pathology changed from Normal to Pathological in participants.tsv
README: Deleted reference to the year (2021), updated link to website, updated reference
----------------------------
FeTA 2.3 - release 17.05.2024
Added a new task for biometry in the derivatives
----------------------------
FeTA 2.4 - release 10.07.2024
In the biometry folder.
- Corrected the biometry for subject 002: LCC was mislabeled, TCD was missing.
- measures.tsv: Corrected the mistake that LCC was labelled as 2 and HV as 1. 
- biometry.tsv: Changed the ordering of the columns to reflect the ordering of the labels.
